properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.name
properties.description: 应用名称.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.version
properties.description: 模块版本.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.owner
properties.description: 应用负责人.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.organization
properties.description: 组织名(BU或部门).

properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.architecture
properties.description: 分层.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.environment
properties.description: 环境，如：dev/test/run.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.application.logger
properties.description: 选择哪种方式输出dubbo内部日志.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.address
properties.description: zookeeper注册中心地址.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.client
properties.description: zookeeper客户端实现，改为默认采用apache的实现.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.username
properties.description: zookeeper注册中心地址的用户名.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.password
properties.description: zookeeper注册中心地址的密码.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.check
properties.description: 启动时检查zookeeper注册中心是否存在.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.register
properties.description: 在zookeeper注册中心上服务是否暴露.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.zkRegistry.subscribe
properties.description: 在zookeeper注册中心上服务是否引用.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.redisRegistry.address
properties.description: reids注册中心地址.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.redisRegistry.password
properties.description: reids注册中心地址的密码.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.redisRegistry.check
properties.description: 启动时检查reids注册中心是否存在.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.redisRegistry.register
properties.description: 在reids注册中心上服务是否暴露.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.redisRegistry.subscribe
properties.description: 在reids注册中心上服务是否引用.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.name
properties.description: dubbo协议的协议名称，默认为dubbo.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.port
properties.description: dubbo协议的服务端口.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.host
properties.description: dubbo协议的服务IP地址(多网卡时使用).

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.threadpool
properties.description: dubbo协议的线程池类型.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.threads
properties.description: dubbo协议的线程池大小(固定大小).

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.iothreads
properties.description: dubbo协议的IO线程池大小(固定大小).

properties.name: spring.dubbo.dubboProtocol.accesslog
properties.description: dubbo协议的访问日志.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.httpProtocol.name
properties.description: http协议的名称，默认为rest.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.httpProtocol.port
properties.description: http协议的服务端口，与必须应用的tomcat端口相同.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.httpProtocol.host
properties.description: dubbo协议的服务IP地址(多网卡时使用).

properties.name: spring.dubbo.httpProtocol.contextpath
properties.description: http协议的上下文路径.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.httpProtocol.server
properties.description: http协议的服务器端实现.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.httpProtocol.accesslog
properties.description: http协议的访问日志.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.monitor.protocol
properties.description: 监控服务的协议，配置registry表示从注册中心查找monitor.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.monitor.address
properties.description: 监控服务的地址，可以配置地址来直连注册中心.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.version
properties.description: 全局版本号，可被服务级配置覆盖.

properties.name: spring.dubbo.group
properties.description: 全局分组，可被服务级配置覆盖.
